Package world.action

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Action
    Abstract class that represents an action that can be executed by a player.
    DropFlagAction
    Action that makes the player drop the flag at its current position.
    IdleAction
    Action that cancels the player's current action.
    MoveAction
    Action that moves the player to the desired destination.
    PickFlagAction
    Action that makes the player pick the flag if he can do it.
    ThrowAction
    Actions that makes the player throw a snowball at the desired destination.
